{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t38-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"方程","title":"针对训练2：参数问题","difficulty":4,"tags":["方程","参数"],"content":"如果关于 $x$ 的方程 $4x - 2m = 3x - 1$ 的解的 $2$ 倍等于与 $2x = 6$ 的解相同，则 $m = $______。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"由 $4x - 2m = 3x - 1$ 得 $x = 2m - 1$\n由 $2x = 6$ 得 $x = 3$\n根据条件：$2(2m - 1) = 3$\n$4m - 2 = 3$\n$m = \\frac{5}{4}$","formula":"m = \\frac{5}{4}"}]},"id":"t38-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}